content.rendered:
Directed by G. Nageswara Reddy.

Written by Diamond Ratna Babu. Rishabh Purohit. G. Nageswara Reddy.

Cast Vishnu Manchu(Arjun). Raj Tarun(Ashwin). Sonarika Bhadoria(Neelaveni). Hebah Patel(Supriya). Rajendra Prasad(Advocate Narayana (as Rajendraprasad)). Krishna Murali Posani(Inspector M. Koteswara Rao). Ravi Babu(Aadi Narayana). Abhimanyu Singh(Gaja). Vennela Kishore(Kishore) .Thagubothu Ramesh.Shakalaka Shankar.Jyoti Singh. Prabhas Sreenu((as Prabhas Srinu)).Sri Sudha.Supreet.Fish Venkat

Language Telugu.

Producers Krishna kishore Garikipati. Sunkara Ramabrahmam.

Production A.K. Entertainments India. AK Entertainments. Goldmines Telefilms.
